headline: LKQ (NASDAQ:LKQ) Misses Q3 Revenue Estimates
summary: Automotive parts company LKQ (NASDAQ:LKQ) fell short of the markets revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, with sales falling 2.4% year on year to $3.50 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.84 per share was 11% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
